English Lyrics - Click Here For English Lyrics

Nalla Nanban vendum endru
andha maranam ninaikindradhaa !!!!
Sirandhavan neethaan endru
unnai kooti sella thudikindradhaa!!!

Iraivaney iraivaney, ivan uyir venduma ?
Engal uyir eduthukol, unnakkadhu podhuma ?
Ivan engal roja chedi, adhai marnam thinbadha ?
Ivan sirththu pesum oli, adhai vendinommeendum thaa?

Ninaivin tharvaarathil,
engal kural konjam kaetka villaya?
Manamin vanathil,
engal niyabagangal pooka villaya?

Iraivaney iraivaney, unnakillai irakkama?
thaai ival azhukural kaeta pinbum urakkama ?

Vaa nanban vaa nanba thozhgalil saayava !!
vazhdhidum naallellaam naan unnai thaangava !!!
